  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="page" n="17">
        <pb n="17"/>
        <lg xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fdc6213ea-2082-4217-b0ac-15875a9144f4.jp2/1580,845,2163,1130/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>A VERY OLD SONG aroused me into life</l>
          <l>when it drove away my low spirits.</l>
          <l>with its royal language.</l>
          <l>A song of a generation silenced</l>
          <l>from the days of old</l>
          <l>aroused me into life.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_B" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2Fdc6213ea-2082-4217-b0ac-15875a9144f4.jp2/1604,2261,2246,1993/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>STANDING on the parted shores of history,</l>
          <l>we still believe what we were taught</l>
          <l>before ever we stood at Sinai:</l>
          <l>that wherever we are, it is eternally Egypt</l>
          <l>that there is a better place, a Promised Land;</l>
          <l>that the winding way to that promise passes</l>
          <l>through the wilderness</l>
          <l>that there is no way to get from here to there</l>
          <l>except by joining hands, marching</l>
          <l>together.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
